'''2016年亚洲室内田径锦标赛'''是第7届[[亚洲室内田径锦标赛|亚洲室内田径锦标赛]]，于2016年2月19日至21日在卡塔尔多哈阿斯拜爾體育館进行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thepeninsulaqatar.com/article/14/01/2016/Qatar-to-host-Asian-Indoor-Athletics-Championship|title=Qatar to host Asian Indoor Athletics Championship|publisher=The Peninsula Qatar|date=2016-01-14|accessdate=2020-09-28|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200928113559/https://www.thepeninsulaqatar.com/article/14/01/2016/Qatar-to-host-Asian-Indoor-Athletics-Championship|archivedate=2020-09-28}}</ref>。

此次比赛中，有三个项目的亚洲纪录及十二个项目的锦标赛纪录被刷新。主办国卡塔尔凭借六枚金牌的成绩位居奖牌榜榜首，获得五枚金牌的中国以及获得四枚金牌的哈萨克斯坦分别位居奖牌榜第二及第三位。<ref name=IAAF1>{{cite web|url=http://www.iaaf.org/news/report/asian-indoor-championships-al-garni-balla|title=Al-Garni clinches second successive double on final day of Asian Indoor Championships|work=IAAF|date=2016-02-21|accessdate=2016-02-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160423230603/http://www.iaaf.org/news/report/asian-indoor-championships-al-garni-balla|archivedate=2016-04-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=IAAF2>{{cite web|url=http://www.iaaf.org/news/report/asian-indoor-championships-al-garni-adekoya|title=Al-Garni and Adekoya in the spotlight on the second day of the Asian Indoor Championships|work=IAAF|date=2016-02-20|accessdate=2016-02-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160423182545/http://www.iaaf.org/news/report/asian-indoor-championships-al-garni-adekoya|archivedate=2016-04-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=IAAF3>{{cite web|url=http://www.iaaf.org/news/report/asian-indoor-championships-2016-barshim-ling|title=Records tumble on first day of Asian Indoor Championships|work=IAAF|date=2016-02-19|accessdate=2016-02-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424212838/http://www.iaaf.org/news/report/asian-indoor-championships-2016-barshim-ling|archivedate=2016-04-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>

